metadata.name: Are you coming or are u just going to stand there?
metadata.description:
This is 1 NFT in a collection of 9 each of which is only edition.  

Size: 4480x6720 px

  You look at her and you seem to understand that she's calling you with her whole appearance, but what's driving her?

Why was it that an hour ago you were fighting over dirty socks in the corner, and now she's ready to role-play with you and submit to you?
